item.description:

[quote=“Aff, post:4, topic:436424”][quote author=Kidpaparoach link=topic=539138.msg3945424#msg3945424 date=1331814287]

[/quote]

there’s also like 3 threads discussing how to get a fire cape, so i don’t see your point

this thread is specific to skyro and the other thread is specific to the OP. please don’t make stupid judgements ty : )[/quote]
It is indeed but he’s done it twice in the past few days whats stopping him from commenting on the other thread saying he wants a team? People read posts on threads do they not, so why would he need a new thread when just as many people if not would read it in the other thread as personally I tend to ignore threads about the same thing. Your the one making the stupid judgement if you never thought about that and don’t insult me, idiot. I say things politely and I get rude replies back -sigh-.

[quote=“Phaze One, post:5, topic:436424”][quote author=Skyro link=topic=539138.msg3945608#msg3945608 date=1331831245]
Sorry but, I really want 80-99 Dungeoneering.
[/quote]

I solo’d 90% of the way to 80 dung. I suggest you do the same[/quote]
Meeeh, I wouldn’t reccomend doing it like that though tbh. You get more xp ph doing larges with a 5 man apart from its hard to find a good team for multiple floors. since he wants to do a lot of dung he should get friends or w.e. and dung long term with them in my opinion but ofc your point is still valid. At lower dung levels it doesn’t make as big a difference.
